## 题目思路
看题解，我也没太懂


## 题目的题解code
```PHP
<?php

class Solution
{
    public function solve($nums, $k)
    {
        $map = [];
        $map[0] = -1;
        $res = count($nums);
        $target = 0;
        $currSum = 0;
        for ($i = 0; $i < count($nums); $i++) {
            $target += $nums[$i];
        }
        $target = $target % $k;
        for ($i = 0; $i < count($nums); $i++) {
            $currSum = ($nums[$i] + $currSum) % $k; // 同余
            $map[$currSum] = $i;
            $prevSum = $this->floorMod($currSum - $target, $k);
            if (isset($map[$prevSum])) {
                $res = min($res, $i -$map[$prevSum]);
            }
        }


        return $res === count($nums) ? -1 : $res;

    }

    private function floorMod($a, $b)
    {
        return (($a % $b) + $b) % $b;
    }
}
```

