# 思路
用前缀和的思想，找到pre[j]和pre[i]之间的关系。为了方便在遍历到j的时候查找前面是否有满足要求的i，用哈希表存储i%k的值，并记录下标。

# 代码
```
import java.util.*;

class Solution {
    public int solve(int[] nums, int k) {
        int sum = 0;
        int n = nums.length;
        int[] pre = new int[n + 1];
        HashMap<Integer, Integer> map = new HashMap<>();

        for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) {
            pre[i] = pre[i - 1] + nums[i - 1];
            sum += nums[i - 1];
        }
        int mod = sum % k;

        if (mod == 0)
            return 0;

        int res = Integer.MAX_VALUE;
        map.put(0, 0);

        for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) {
            int j = pre[i];
            int t = j % k;
            int q = (t + k - mod) % k;
            if (map.containsKey(q) && i - map.get(q) != nums.length) {
                res = Math.min(res, i - map.get(q));
            }
            map.put(t, i);
        }

        return res == Integer.MAX_VALUE ? -1 : res;
    }
}
```

