## 思路
二分查找，low，high指针。根据(low+high)>>2，来得到mid，然后与target比较。
## 代码
```python
class Solution:
    def searchInsert(self, nums: List[int], target: int) -> int:
        low = 0
        high = len(nums) - 1
        mid = (low + high) // 2
        while low <= high:
            if nums[mid] == target:
                return mid
            elif nums[mid] < target:
                low = mid + 1
                mid = (low + high) // 2
            elif nums[mid] > target:
                high = mid - 1
                mid = (low + high) // 2
        return low
```
