### 思路

先将链表变成环形链表，找到倒数第k个node当作新head。

### 代码


```java
class Solution {
    public ListNode rotateRight(ListNode head, int k) {
        if(head == null || k == 0) {
            return head;
        }
        int len = 0;
        ListNode tail = head; 
        //找到linked list的尾部和长度
        while(tail.next != null) {
            tail = tail.next;
            len++;
        }
        len++; //还要后移一位才是总长度
        tail.next = head; //让tail指向head，首尾相连
        k %= len; //k可能比length大
        ListNode newHead = null;
        for(int i = 0; i < len - k - 1; i++) {
            head = head.next;
        }//此时head是第len-k个node，
        newHead = head.next;
        head.next = null;
        return newHead;
    }
}

```

