### 思路

快慢指针找链表中点，然后通过递归得到左子树和右子树。

### 代码

``` Java
class Solution {
    public TreeNode sortedListToBST(ListNode head) {
        if(head == null) {
            return null;
        } 
        if(head != null && head.next == null) {
            return new TreeNode(head.val);
        }
        ListNode dummy = head;
        ListNode slow = head;
        ListNode fast = head;
        ListNode pre = null;
        while(fast != null && fast.next != null) {
            pre = slow;
            slow = slow.next;
            fast = fast.next.next;
        }
        pre.next = null;
        TreeNode root = new TreeNode(slow.val);
        root.left = sortedListToBST(dummy);
        root.right = sortedListToBST(slow.next);
        return root;
    }
}
```

**复杂度**

- 时间复杂度：O(nlogn)，其中 n 是链表的节点数量
  - n + 2 * n/2 + 4 * n/4 + ... + n * n/n = n * logn (二叉树的高度为logn)
- 空间复杂度：O(logn) 递归的深度

### 思路

1. 计算出a,b的长度差，让长一点的链表先移动到两者长度相同的位置然后开始找相同的node。
2. 改进：假设链表A =  a + c, 链表B = b + c, 让两者都移动a + b + c次, 最后都会停在interact point。

### 代码

``` Java
public class Solution {
    public ListNode getIntersectionNode(ListNode headA, ListNode headB) {
        int lenA = 0;
        int lenB = 0;
        ListNode a = headA;
        ListNode b = headB;
        while(a.next != null) {
            a = a.next;
            lenA++;
        }
        while(b.next != null) {
            b = b.next;
            lenB++;
        }
        a = lenA > lenB ? headA : headB;
        b = lenA > lenB ? headB : headA;
        int n = Math.abs(lenA - lenB);
        while(n > 0) {
            a = a.next;
            n--;
        }
        while(a != b) {
            a = a.next;
            b = b.next;
        }
        return a;
    }
}
```

