示例 1：

输入：head = [1,2,3,4,5], k = 2
输出：[4,5,1,2,3]


示例 2：

输入：head = [0,1,2], k = 4
输出：[2,0,1]


 

提示：

链表中节点的数目在范围 [0, 500] 内
-100 <= Node.val <= 100
0 <= k <= 2 * 109
## 代码

- 语言支持：JavaScript

JavaScript Code:

```javascript

var rotateRight = function(head, k) {
    if (k === 0 || !head || !head.next) {
        return head;
    }
    let n = 1;
    let cur = head;
    while (cur.next) {
        cur = cur.next;
        n++;
    }

    let add = n - k % n;
    if (add === n) {
        return head;
    }

    cur.next = head;
    while (add) {
        cur = cur.next;
        add--;
    }

    const ret = cur.next;
    cur.next = null;
    return ret;
};


```


