### 思路
从个位数求两数之和，carry= 1 如果sum大于10.
sum % 10 得到的结果就是当位数的值
while 结束loop如果num[]里没有元素，而且k 等于0

### 代码

```java
public List<Integer> addToArrayForm(int[] num, int k) {
        List<Integer> res = new ArrayList<>();
        int carry = 0;
        int l1 = num.length -1;
        while (l1 >= 0 || k != 0){
            int a = l1 < 0 ? 0 : num[l1]; //get last element in num[]
            int b = k <= 0 ? 0 : k % 10; //get last digit in k            
            int sum = a + b + carry;
            res.add(0, sum % 10);
            carry = sum / 10;
            
            l1--;
            k /= 10;
        }
        if (carry != 0) res.add(0,carry);
    
        return res;     
    }

```

