### 思路
用stack实现CustomStack
inc[] 用来存储increment value,每pop一个值，加上inc[i]的值返回，inc[i-1]=inc[i],以便后面pop时可以加上increment value值

### 代码

```Java
class CustomStack {
    int n;
    int[] inc;
    Stack<Integer> stack;

    public CustomStack(int maxSize) {
        n = maxSize;
        inc = new int[n];
        stack =  new Stack<>();
    }

    public void push(int x) {
        if( stack.size() < n){
            stack.push(x);
        }
    }

    public int pop() {
        int i = stack.size() - 1;
        if(i < 0 )return -1;
        if(i > 0){
            inc[i-1] += inc[i]; //store the increment value for bottom use
        }
        int res = stack.pop() + inc[i];
        inc[i] = 0; //set current increment to 0 since its poped
        return res;
    }

    public void increment(int k, int val) {
        int i = Math.min(k, stack.size()) - 1;
        if(i >= 0)
            inc[i] += val; //inc[i] means increment val for all stack[0]-> stack[i]

    }
}

```

