### 思路
1.求size, tail
2.找到cutoff节点，用curr node标记第一段最后一个node
3. swap 两段位置： 
        tail.next = head; 
        head = curr.next; //new head 
        curr.next = null;

### 代码


```java
public ListNode rotateRight(ListNode head, int k) {
        //edge case check
        if(head == null) return head;

        ListNode tail = head;
        int size = 1;
        while(tail.next != null){
            tail = tail.next;
            size++;
        }

        //k might be greater than size
        k = k % size;

        ListNode curr = head;
        int n = 0;
        while(n < size-k-1){
            curr = curr.next;
            n++;
        }

        tail.next = head; 
        head = curr.next; //new head 
        curr.next = null;

        return head;

    }


```

