### 思路

定义两个指针l1, l2,分别指向headA, headB
     - while l1, l2的值不等，既没有焦点：
           1. l1 not null, go to next node, else go to the other list head
           2. l1 not null, go to next node, else go to the other list head
    - loop breaks, return l1
logic: nodes of headA + nodes of headB = nodes of headB + nodes of headA, 所以注定会相遇，要么在末尾null, 要么在中途某个node



### 代码

```java
public ListNode getIntersectionNode(ListNode headA, ListNode headB) {
        if(headA == null || headB == null) return null;

        ListNode l1 = headA;
        ListNode l2 = headB;

        while( l1 != l2){
            l1 = l1 == null ? headB : l1.next;
            l2 = l2 == null ? headA : l2.next;
        }
        return l1;      
    }


