### 题目：【Day 2】821. 字符的最短距离
[821. 字符的最短距离](https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/shortest-distance-to-a-character/)

### 思路1
1. 新建列表存放字符 c 存在的位置
2. 在 result 列表中，存放两次循环找出的最小 diff 距离

```python
class Solution:
    def shortestToChar(self, s: str, c: str) -> List[int]:
        L = []
        result = []
        for i in range(len(s)):
            if s[i] == c:
                L.append(i)
        for i in range(len(s)):
            diff = 10000
            for j in L:
                if (abs(j - i)) < diff:
                    diff = abs(j - i)
            result.append(diff)
        return result
