## 题目地址(989. 数组形式的整数加法)

https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/add-to-array-form-of-integer/

## 思路

- 从后向前逐位相加

## 关键点

-  不能直接把num转成数字相加，数字过大时会越界被截取
-  考虑进位
-  考虑k的长度大于num

## 代码

- 语言支持：JavaScript

JavaScript Code:

```javascript

/**
 * @param {number[]} num
 * @param {number} k
 * @return {number[]}
 */
var addToArrayForm = function(num, k) {
    let add = k
    for (let i=num.length-1;i>=0;i--) {
        if(!add) {
          break;
        }
        let sum = num[i] + add%10
        add = Math.floor(add/10)
        if (sum >= 10) {
            add++
            num[i] = sum%10
        } else {
          num[i] = sum
        }
    }
    while(add > 0) {
        num.unshift(add%10)
        add = Math.floor(add/10)
    }
    return num
};

```


