## 题目
数组形式的整数加法
https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/add-to-array-form-of-integer/submissions/
## 思路
   - 由于直接循环将数组取出来相加长度可能会超出，所以按倒序取出数组，依次相加取余放进数组
   - 可能会出现加完后k值为个位数的情况，所以多加个判断，将剩余数也加入数组
## C++代码
``` class Solution {
public:
    vector<int> addToArrayForm(vector<int>& num, int k) {
        reverse(num.begin(), num.end());
        int t = k, idx=0;
        vector<int> ans;
        while(t)
        {
            if(idx<num.size()) t+=num[idx++];
            ans.push_back(t%10);
            t /= 10;
        }
        while(idx<num.size()) ans.push_back(num[idx++]);
        reverse(ans.begin(), ans.end());
        return ans;

    }
};
