## 思路
用栈处理[]的嵌套，每次处理完]后将结果入栈，最终结果将栈清空

## 代码
```java
public String decodeString(String s) {
        int i = 0, n = s.length();
        Stack<String> stack = new Stack<>();
        while (i < n){
            if(s.charAt(i) >= '0' && s.charAt(i) <= '9') {
                int left = i;
                while (s.charAt(i) >= '0' && s.charAt(i) <= '9') {
                    i++;
                }
                stack.push(s.substring(left, i));
            }
            if (s.charAt(i) >= 'a' && s.charAt(i) <= 'z'){
                int left = i;
                while (i < n && s.charAt(i) >= 'a' && s.charAt(i) <= 'z') {
                    i++;
                }
                stack.push(s.substring(left, i));
                if(i == n) break;
            }
            if (s.charAt(i)=='['){
                stack.push("[");
                i++;
                if(i == n) break;
            }
            if (s.charAt(i)==']'){
                StringBuffer tmp1 = new StringBuffer();
                while(!stack.peek().equals("[")){
                    tmp1 = tmp1.insert(0, stack.pop());
                }
                stack.pop();//"["
                int times = Integer.parseInt(stack.pop());
                StringBuffer tmp2 = new StringBuffer();
                for(int ic = 0; ic < times; ic++)
                    tmp2 = tmp2.insert(0, tmp1);//字符串插入自身会导致指数级增大,因此使用两个变量
                stack.push(tmp2.toString());
                i++;
            }
        }
        StringBuffer ans = new StringBuffer();
        while (!stack.empty())
            ans.insert(0, stack.pop());
        return ans.toString();
    }
```

## 思路
用一个逆序和一个正序的栈，具体将数据存在正序还是逆序栈决定了push和pop方法的性能，由于有peek方法，选择将数据存储在逆序栈中

## 代码
```java
class MyQueue {
    Deque<Integer> stackReverse = new LinkedList<>();
    Deque<Integer> stackTmp = new LinkedList<>();

    public MyQueue() {

    }

    public void push(int x) {
        while (!stackReverse.isEmpty())
            stackTmp.push(stackReverse.pop());
        stackTmp.push(x);
        while (!stackTmp.isEmpty())
            stackReverse.push(stackTmp.pop());
    }

    public int pop() {
        if(!stackReverse.isEmpty())
            return stackReverse.poll();
        else return -1;
    }

    public int peek() {
        if(!stackReverse.isEmpty())
            return stackReverse.peek();
        else return -1;
    }

    public boolean empty() {
        return stackReverse.isEmpty();
    }
}
```

## 思路
最开始想到的是窗口法，左部分序列的最大值小于右部分序列的最小值就能划分，另最左边的值为最小值，最右边的值为最大值时都可以被划分，但是没能想出比较简洁的写法，题解的计数排序的思路比较清晰，感觉会比较适合面试

## 代码
```java
public int maxChunksToSorted(int[] arr) {
        int chunkNumber = 0, n = arr.length;
        int[] arrSort = (int[])arr.clone();
        Arrays.sort(arrSort);
        HashMap<Integer, Integer> map = new HashMap<>();
        int nonzero = 0;
        for(int i = 0; i < n; i++){
            int x = arr[i];
            int y = arrSort[i];
            map.put(x, map.getOrDefault(x, 0) + 1);
            if(map.get(x) == 0) nonzero--;
            if(map.get(x) == 1) nonzero++;

            map.put(y, map.getOrDefault(y, 0) - 1);
            if(map.get(y) == 0) nonzero--;
            if(map.get(y) == -1) nonzero++;

            if(nonzero == 0) chunkNumber++;
        }
        return chunkNumber;
    }
```

## 思路
使用快慢指针，快指针先走k步，快慢指针一起走到快指针到头，快指针指向原链表头，慢指针指向变成新链表头（被虐了几天终于能AC一道题了）

## 代码
```java
public ListNode rotateRight(ListNode head, int k) {
        if(head == null) return null;
        ListNode fast = head, slow = head, headCopy = head;
        for(int i = 0; i < k; i++){//防止k大于链表长度，可以改成先求链表长度再求余的形式
            if(fast.next != null)
                fast = fast.next;
            else
                fast = head;
        }
        while (fast.next != null){
            fast = fast.next;
            slow = slow.next;
        }
        fast.next = headCopy;
        ListNode newHead = slow.next;
        slow.next = null;
        return newHead;
    }
```

## 思路
同样是快慢指针法，但需要额外的指针指向慢指针的前驱方便交换，另外链表的长度为奇数或偶数时都需要做判别

## 代码
```java
public ListNode swapPairs(ListNode head) {
        if(head == null) return null;
        if(head.next == null) return head;
        ListNode preHead = new ListNode();
        preHead.next = head;
        ListNode pre = preHead, slow = head, fast = head.next;
        while(true){
            pre.next = fast;
            slow.next = fast.next;
            fast.next = slow;

            if(slow.next != null)
                slow = slow.next;
            else return preHead.next;
            if(slow.next != null)
                fast = slow.next;
            else return preHead.next;
            pre = pre.next.next;
        }
    }
