## 142. 环形链表 II
## 思路
- 链表是否有环
  - slow、fast 指针可相遇，说明链表有环
- 如何寻找环的入口
  - 从头节点发出一个指针，再从 slow、fast 相遇节点发出一个指针
  - 两个指针不断往前走（每次走一个节点）
  - 两个指针在环的入口相遇
<img width="389" alt="image" src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/51183663/162776567-24f7b0e2-5cac-46df-a711-e0069299d62f.png">

slow pointer moved steps * 2 = fast pointer moved steps
```
(x + y) * 2 = x + y + n(y + z)
x = n(y + z) - y
x = (n - 1)(y + z) + z
```
> 从相遇点到入环点的距离 z，加上 n-1 圈的环长(y + z)，等于从链表头部到入环点的距离 x


## 复杂度
- 时间：O(N)
- 空间：O(1)

## 代码
```javascript
/**
 * Definition for singly-linked list.
 * function ListNode(val) {
 *     this.val = val;
 *     this.next = null;
 * }
 */

/**
 * @param {ListNode} head
 * @return {ListNode}
 */
var detectCycle = function(head) {
    var slow = head;
    var fast = head;
    while (fast && fast.next) {
        slow = slow.next;
        fast = fast.next.next;
        if (fast == slow) {
            var cycleFinder = head;
            while (slow != cycleFinder) {
                slow = slow.next;
                cycleFinder = cycleFinder.next;
            }
            return cycleFinder;
        }
    }
    return null;
};
```

## LRU
## 基本思路
- 查询/修改过的节点，要提前到头部
  - 哈希查询 O(1)
  - 链表查询 O(N), 头部增删 O(1)
  - 综上，哈希表用于存放节点地址，链表用于修改节点

## 复杂度
- 时间：O(1)
- 空间：O(capacity) 
## 代码
```javascript
/**
 * @param {number} capacity
 */
var LRUCache = function(capacity) {
    this.cacheMap = {};
    this.linkedList = new DLinkedList(capacity);
};

var Node = function(key, value) {
    this.prev = null;
    this.next = null;
    this.key = key;
    this.value = value;
}

var DLinkedList = function(capacity) {
    this.front = new Node();
    this.rear = new Node(); 
    this.front.next = this.rear;
    this.rear.prev = this.front;
    this.capacity = capacity;
    this.size = 0;
};

DLinkedList.prototype.addFront = function(node) {
    node.prev = this.front;
    node.next = this.front.next;
    this.front.next.prev = node;
    this.front.next = node;
};

DLinkedList.prototype.moveToFront = function(node) {
    this.deleteNode(node);
    this.addFront(node);
};

DLinkedList.prototype.deleteNode = function(node) {
    node.next.prev = node.prev;
    node.prev.next = node.next;
};

DLinkedList.prototype.deleteRear = function() {
    var rear = this.rear.prev;
    this.deleteNode(rear);
    return rear;
};


/** 
 * @param {number} key
 * @return {number}
 */
LRUCache.prototype.get = function(key) {
    var node = this.cacheMap[key];
    if (node) {
        this.linkedList.moveToFront(node);
        return node.value;
    } else {
        return -1;
    }
};

/** 
 * @param {number} key 
 * @param {number} value
 * @return {void}
 */
LRUCache.prototype.put = function(key, value) {
    var node = this.cacheMap[key];
    if (node) {
        node.value = value;
        this.linkedList.moveToFront(node);
    } else {
        var newNode = new Node(key, value);
        this.linkedList.addFront(newNode);
        this.cacheMap[key] = newNode;
        if (this.linkedList.size == this.linkedList.capacity) {
            var rear = this.linkedList.deleteRear();
            delete this.cacheMap[rear.key];     
        } else {
            this.linkedList.size++;
        }
    }
};

/**
 * Your LRUCache object will be instantiated and called as such:
 * var obj = new LRUCache(capacity)
 * var param_1 = obj.get(key)
 * obj.put(key,value)
 */
```

