## 思路
使用非"]"的字符入栈，遇到"]"时，字符出栈，在遇到"["之前出栈的字符拼接得repeatString，随后数字字符出栈拼接转化成对应数字就是repeatNum，根据上述两个变量，得到重复的完整字符串，随后压入栈重复上述操作。

## 代码
```
 var decodeString = function(s) {
    let stack = [];
    for(let c of s){
        if(c !== ']'){
            stack.push(c);
            continue;
        }
        let repeatString = '';
        while(stack.length > 0 && stack[stack.length - 1] != '['){
            repeatString = stack.pop() + repeatString;
        }

        /* 弹出[ */
        stack.pop();

        let repeatNum = '';
        while(stack.length > 0 && !isNaN(stack[stack.length - 1])){
            repeatNum = stack.pop() + repeatNum;
        }
        stack.push(repeatString.repeat(Number(repeatNum)));
    }
    return stack.join('');
};
```
