## 思路
总的思路是将倒数step个节点移至链表头部  
使用快慢指针：  
1、获取链表长度length  
2、取余数step，利用余数自减，快指针移至第step + 1个节点（因为初始fast = head）  
3、快慢指针同时走，快指针走到尾时，慢指针走到倒数第step+1个节点（因为初始slow = head）

## 代码
```
 var rotateRight = function(head, k) {
    if(head === null || head.next === null){
        return head;
    }
    //获取链表长度
    let length = 0;
    let temp = head;
    while(temp !== null){
        length += 1;
        temp = temp.next;
    }

    let step = k % length;
    let fast = head;
    let slow = head;
    while(step > 0){
        fast = fast.next;
        step -= 1;
    }

    while(fast.next !== null){
        fast = fast.next;
        slow = slow.next;
    }
    fast.next = head;
    head = slow.next;
    slow.next = null;
    return head;
};
```
