## Idea
Use two array (pre & after)
pre stores the max element before each arr[i]
after stores the min element before each arr[i]
Compare pre and after, if the pre[i] <= after[i+1] meaning all elements in arr[0, i] are <= all elements in arr[i+1, n-1], which could be split. res++

