### 思路

遍历 

- 是数字，将数字整体进栈（数字范围1-300）

- 是"["进栈 

- 是字母 进栈

- 是']'开始出栈 直到'['

  对出栈的[]中间的字符串 按顺序反转后组成新字符串。此时取栈顶（必是数字），次数相乘。

  结果再放入栈

再重复遍历

### 代码

```java
public static String decodeString(String s) {
    Stack<String> stack = new Stack<>();
    String num = "";    //用于拼接的字符串
    char[] chars = s.toCharArray();


    for (int i = 0; i < chars.length; i++){
        char c = chars[i];
        if (Character.isDigit(c)){
            num = num + c;
        }else if (c == '['){
            stack.push(num);
            num = "";
            stack.push("[");
        }else if (Character.isLetter(c)){
            stack.push(c+"");
        }else if (c == ']'){
            LinkedList<String> sub = new LinkedList<String>();
            String temp = "";
            while (!stack.isEmpty()){
                temp = stack.pop();
                if ("[".equals(temp)){
                    break;
                }
                sub.addLast(temp);
            }
            Collections.reverse(sub);
            String o = getString(sub);
            stack.push(multStr(o,Integer.parseInt(stack.pop())));

        }
    }

    String result = "";
    String[] strings = new String[stack.size()];
    int i = 0;
    while (!stack.isEmpty()){
        strings[i] = stack.pop();
        i++;
    }
    for(i = strings.length-1; i >= 0; i--){
        result = result + strings[i];
    }
    return result;
}

public static String getString(LinkedList<String> v) {
    StringBuffer ret = new StringBuffer();
    for (String s : v) {
        ret.append(s);
    }
    return ret.toString();
}


public static String multStr(String str,int num){
    String result = "";
    for (int i = 0; i < num; i++){

        result += str;
    }
    return result;
}
```



