### 思路

对两个树递归遍历比较值是否相等

只有相等才继续向下递归

### 代码

```java
    public boolean isSameTree(TreeNode p, TreeNode q) {
        return process(p,q);
    }

    private boolean process(TreeNode p, TreeNode q) {

        if (p == null && q == null){
            return true;
        }

        if (p == null || q == null){
            return false;
        }

        if (p.val == q.val){
            return process(p.left,q.left)&&process(p.right,q.right);
        }else {
            return false;
        }
    }
```



