## 思路
维护一个栈 和临时链表来进行括号匹配和字符串储存，当遇到右括号开始pop计算后形成新字符串，然后重新入栈


## 代码
```

class Solution {
    public String decodeString(String s) {
        int len = s.length();
        StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();
        Stack<Character> st = new Stack<>();
        for(int i = 0; i < len;i++){
            
            char t = s.charAt(i);
            if(t == ']'){                   
                List<Character> temp = new ArrayList<>();
                while(st.peek()!='['){
                    temp.add(st.pop());
                   } 
                
                    st.pop(); // remove the '['
                    int base =1;
                    int k = 0;
                    while( !st.empty() && Character.isDigit(st.peek() )){
                         k = k + (st.pop() - '0' ) * base;
                         base *= 10;
                    }

                    while(k!=0){
                        for(int j = temp.size() -1; j >=0;j--){
                            st.push(temp.get(j));
                        }
                        k--;
                    }
                
            }else{
                st.push(t);
            }
        
        }
        char[] ans = new char[st.size()];
        int j = st.size()-1;
        while(!st.empty()){
            ans[j] = st.pop();
            j--;
        }

        
        return new String(ans);
    }
}

```
