## 思路
先统计有多少个数据，再通过k%len 得到需要的步数。使用双指针进行快慢K，来达到效果

## 代码

```
class Solution {
    public ListNode rotateRight(ListNode head, int k) {
        if(head == null || head.next == null) return head;
        
        int len = 0;
        ListNode p = head;
        while(p != null){
            p = p.next;
            len++;
        }
        
        k = k % len;
        ListNode s = head, f = head;
        
        while(f.next!=null){
            
            if( k <= 0){
                s= s.next;
                
            }
            k--;
            f= f.next;
                
        }
        f.next = head;
        ListNode res  = s.next;
        s.next = null;
        return res;
        
    }
}
```

