### 思路

先计算链表长度，与k取模后得到真正需要旋转的次数，但是并不需要真的旋转这么多次。
而是利用快慢指针直接找到旋转n次后的那个新的头节点，从该处断后，最后将原链表尾
指向原链表头即可

### 代码


```Go
func rotateRight(head *ListNode, k int) *ListNode {
	if head == nil {return head}

	var listLen int
	var p1 = head
	for p1 != nil {
		listLen++
		p1 = p1.Next
	}

	diff := k % listLen
	if diff == 0 {
		return head
	}
	p2 := head
	p1 = head
	for i := 0; i < diff; i++ {
		p1 = p1.Next
	}
	for p1.Next != nil {
		p1 = p1.Next
		p2 = p2.Next
	}

	newHead := p2.Next
	p2.Next = nil
	p1.Next = head
	return newHead
}

```

